be served twice per month. Resident income must be below 200% of the federal poverty guidelines. 

Intake Process: Walk-in & drive up for pick up.

Documents: New clients must provide ID for each member of the household. Photo ID (driver’s license or state ID) for adults. Birth certificates, Social Security cards or school IDs for children. Proof of current address (lease or utility bills received by mail).
